name: "Cow Puncher"
description:
RLP is a London based artist & writer. Using covers from 1920s American comics as a foundation, he attempts to take ideas from the pop art movement combined with the dynamic layering of colours to update & revitalise the action unfolding on the page.

Giclée print on Hahnemuhle German Etching Paper.

Edition of 21.

Signed by artist.

34 x 26cm

10% of sale price is donated to The Anne Rowling Regenerative Neurology Clinic:
http://www.annerowlingclinic.com/

(Free Postage. Please allow 1-2 weeks for delivery)
